name: Prizeo
long_description:
Prizeo is a charitable fundraising platform that enables celebrities and influencers to fundraise for their favorite causes through the offering of money-can't-buy prize experiences and rewards to their fans and the general public. 

Find out more by visiting prizeo.com and following @prizeo on Twitter.
